e;\">defying its customers\' expectations that the best programmers are in places like Silicon Valley.  <span class=\"apple-style-span\">Today, the company boasts over 20 developers and builds businesses for startups all over the country.  They are</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; color: #242424; background: none repeat scroll 0% 0% white;\"> looking to hire more talented individuals in the Charlotte area.  Bring a resume!</span></p>',73,'2011-11-02 15:00:00','2011-11-02 17:00:00',0,'images/avatar/events/6b000a41635c059a5b7272dc.png','images/avatar/events/thumb_6b000a41635c059a5b7272dc.png',0,2,0,0,0,30,1,'2011-10-27 15:37:22',128,1,255,255,'Ameri','',0,NULL,'0000-00-00',NULL,NULL),(112,0,5,3,'group','James Martin Middle School - Parent\'s Night','James Martin Middle School, 7800 IBM Drive,  Charlotte, NC','<p>James Martin Middle School is hosting a Parents\' Night on November 9th from 6:00 - 7:30.  This will be a fair style event, where we will have a table to demonstrate what STARS can do.  This is a very large middle school with about 1500 students and they will set you up in a large classroom or hallway to explain the demonstration.</p>\r\n<p>We need at least 1 volunteer from both the Game Design and Robotics teams to give demonstrations on each.  JMMS is expecting quality activities or demonstrations showing what students can do in Game Design and Robotics, so work with your teams on developing a great activity on each.  This is an excellent opportunity to reach a very large audience!</p>\r\n<p>This event is coming up very soon, so we need commitments by Friday, November 3rd.  I will prompt you about this again in class.</p>\r\n<p> </p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: #000000; font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: x-small;\"><span style=\"line-height: normal;\"><br /></span></span></p>',77,'2011-11-09 18:00:00','2011-11-09 19:30:00',0,NULL,NULL,0,2,0,0,0,0,1,'2011-11-03 14:51:12',101,1,35.2986,-80.767,'Ameri','',0,NULL,'0000-00-00',NULL,NULL),(115,0,