0.917969); padding-left: 30px;\"><span style=\"color: #222222;\"> </span></div>\r\n<div style=\"color: #222222; font-family: Arial; font-size: 11px; line-height: normal; background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.917969); padding-left: 30px;\"><span style=\"color: #222222;\">We are excited to offer an excellent opportunity to organizations in the area for outreach to our students.  We have received a Bright Ideas grant from our local Touchstone Energy Cooperative to involve the community in the learning that is taking place at J.N. Fries Magnet School.  We have over 200 sixth, seventh and eighth grade students that are excited to learn about opportunities that lie ahead for them in the fields of science, engineering, math and technologies.  To help them succeed in the quest we would like to invite you to present at our Future Fair to showcase opportunities available both now and in the future.  The fair will be held at J.N. Fries Middle School on February 29<span style=\"font-size: xx-small;\"><span style=\"font-size: 5.3pt;\"><sup>th</sup></span></span> from 11:30 a.m. until 1:20 p.m.</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"color: #222222; font-family: Arial; font-size: 11px; line-height: normal; background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.917969); padding-left: 30px;\"><span style=\"color: #222222;\">This is a wonderful chance for you to come and share all of the wonderful things your business and/or career has to offer for these students.  Many of our students are researching different careers and avenues to take for that career.  We would love for you to come and share your perspective. </span></div>\r\n<div style=\"color: #222222; font-family: Arial; font-size: 11px; line-height: normal; background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.917969); padding-left: 30px;\"><span style=\"color: #222222;\">If you or someone you know has a related career and would be interested in showcasing that career or company to the students, please contact Tracy LeCompte at <a href=\"mailto:tracy.lecompte@ca